<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0"/>
  <title>Verify Your Account - Meesho</title>
  <style>
    * { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }
    body {
      font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
      background-color: #f5f5f5;
      padding: 30px 10px;
    }
    .wrapper {
      max-width: 560px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      background: #ffffff;
      border-radius: 16px;
      overflow: hidden;
      box-shadow: 0 4px 24px rgba(0,0,0,0.10);
    }
    /* Header */
    .header {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f43397 0%, #ff6b6b 100%);
      padding: 36px 40px 28px;
      text-align: center;
    }
    .header .logo {
      font-size: 32px;
      font-weight: 800;
      color: #ffffff;
      letter-spacing: 1px;
    }
    .header .logo span {
      color: #ffe3f0;
    }
    .header .tagline {
      font-size: 13px;
      color: rgba(255,255,255,0.85);
      margin-top: 4px;
      letter-spacing: 0.5px;
    }
    /* Body */
    .body {
      padding: 36px 40px;
    }
    .greeting {
      font-size: 22px;
      font-weight: 700;
      color: #1a1a2e;
      margin-bottom: 12px;
    }
    .message {
      font-size: 15px;
      color: #555;
      line-height: 1.7;
      margin-bottom: 30px;
    }
    /* OTP Box */
    .otp-label {
      font-size: 13px;
      font-weight: 600;
      color: #f43397;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: 1.5px;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
    }
    .otp-box {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #fff0f8 0%, #fff5f0 100%);
      border: 2px dashed #f43397;
      border-radius: 14px;
      padding: 22px 10px;
      text-align: center;
      margin-bottom: 28px;
    }
    .otp-code {
      font-size: 48px;
      font-weight: 900;
      letter-spacing: 14px;
      color: #f43397;
      font-family: 'Courier New', monospace;
    }
    .otp-expiry {
      font-size: 12px;
      color: #999;
      margin-top: 8px;
    }
    /* Info box */
    .info-box {
      background: #fff8f0;
      border-left: 4px solid #ff6b6b;
      border-radius: 8px;
      padding: 14px 18px;
      margin-bottom: 28px;
    }
    .info-box p {
      font-size: 13px;
      color: #666;
      line-height: 1.6;
    }
    .info-box strong {
      color: #f43397;
    }
    /* Steps */
    .steps-title {
      font-size: 14px;
      font-weight: 700;
      color: #1a1a2e;
      margin-bottom: 12px;
    }
    .step {
      display: flex;
      align-items: flex-start;
      gap: 12px;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
    }
    .step-num {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f43397, #ff6b6b);
      color: white;
      width: 22px;
      height: 22px;
      border-radius: 50%;
      font-size: 12px;
      font-weight: 700;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      flex-shrink: 0;
      margin-top: 1px;
    }
    .step p {
      font-size: 13px;
      color: #555;
      line-height: 1.5;
    }
    /* Divider */
    .divider {
      border: none;
      border-top: 1px solid #f0f0f0;
      margin: 28px 0;
    }
    /* Footer */
    .footer {
      background: #fafafa;
      padding: 24px 40px;
      text-align: center;
      border-top: 1px solid #f0f0f0;
    }
    .footer .brand {
      font-size: 18px;
      font-weight: 800;
      color: #f43397;
      margin-bottom: 6px;
    }
    .footer p {
      font-size: 12px;
      color: #aaa;
      line-height: 1.6;
    }
    .footer .social {
      margin-top: 14px;
      font-size: 12px;
      color: #ccc;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="wrapper">

    <!-- Header -->
    <div class="header">
      <div class="logo">meesho<span>.</span></div>
      <div class="tagline">India's #1 Social Commerce Platform</div>
    </div>

    <!-- Body -->
    <div class="body">
      <div class="greeting">Hello, <%= name %> 👋</div>
      <p class="message">
        Welcome to <strong>Meesho</strong>! We're excited to have you on board.<br/>
        Use the OTP below to verify your account and get started.
      </p>

      <div class="otp-label">Your One-Time Password</div>
      <div class="otp-box">
        <div class="otp-code"><%= otp %></div>
        <div class="otp-expiry">⏱ This OTP expires in <strong>5 minutes</strong></div>
      </div>

      <div class="info-box">
        <p>⚠️ <strong>Never share this OTP</strong> with anyone. Meesho will never ask for your OTP via call or message. If you did not register, please ignore this email.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="steps-title">How to verify:</div>
      <div class="step">
        <div class="step-num">1</div>
        <p>Go back to the Meesho app or website</p>
      </div>
      <div class="step">
        <div class="step-num">2</div>
        <p>Enter the 6-digit OTP shown above</p>
      </div>
      <div class="step">
        <div class="step-num">3</div>
        <p>Your account will be verified instantly ✅</p>
      </div>

      <hr class="divider"/>
      <p style="font-size:13px; color:#aaa; text-align:center;">
        Didn't request this? You can safely ignore this email.
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- Footer -->
    <div class="footer">
      <div class="brand">meesho</div>
      <p>© 2024 Meesho Inc. All rights reserved.<br/>
        Bangalore, Karnataka, India
      </p>
      <div class="social">Made for Indian entrepreneurs</div>
    </div>

  </div>
</body>
</html>
